data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET due to buyer's financing. Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom home in Springfield. With a partially finished walkout basement with a bedroom and extra living space and storage, this property offers flexibility and space for your family's needs. The prime location with a short commute to Nashville adds to its appeal. Notable features include a roof and hot water heater both installed in 2018, providing peace of mind. Don't miss out! Property to be sold as is. Cash or Conventional loan only.
